Update:

-- Total Pricing -
1. DataFlow ( assuming 1 TB streaming data ) = $2.16
2. Cloud Storage = $ 20.38
3. BigQuery General ( no ML or visualization ) for all types of storage = 152.81 USD

Points to Note -
1. All the costing provide is given for 1 TB ONLY.
2. Monthly charges are mentioned.
3. In BigQuery, we might need to remove different type of storage available, but just to see bigger picture I took all the things into consideration.
4. For API hosting, Pub/Sub & Firebase, will connect with Nikhil to discuss in detail.

-- Playing around with Slack Export, will keep you posted on it.
